<concept id="concept_B32294CC9FA643A2A14A74B1DAA49C95" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Creating a Certificate</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>The following command creates a certificate: </p>
            <p>
                <codeblock>%JAVA_HOME%\bin\keytool -genkey -alias tpcert -keysize 1024 
-keystore keystore.jks</codeblock>
            </p>
            <p>You will be prompted for a password for the <codeph>keystore.jks</codeph> keystore that will be created containing the certificate identified by the alias <codeph>tpcert</codeph>. In addition, you need to specify detailed information on your organization and its location. </p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
